  <description>
    <p>A simple application for encoding and decoding text. Hide your text from prying eyes!
    <br>
    <b>Note:</b> This application does not actually encrypt files. This was made just enchipers strings. Have fun!
    </p>
    <p>Supported Ciphers</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Caesar Shift</li>
      <li>Atbash</li>
      <li>ROT13</li>
      <li>Ascii</li>
      <li>Base64</li>
      <li>Polybius Square</li>
      <li>Hashing Functions (md5, sha1, sha256)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Upcoming Features</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Bifid Cipher</li>
      <li>Vigenere Cipher</li>
      <li>Beaufort cipher</li>
    </ul>
